
* Dissertation: The Haunting Author in the Distribution of Ownership and Authority: An exploration through Collaborative Cultural Production. By [[Shun-Ling Chen]].


=Description=

"In this dissertation, she studies how narrowly collaboration is contrued in the "joint work" doctrine in US copyright law, then contrasts that with large-scale and continuous collaborative efforts in online peer-production communities and in indigenous/marginalized communities with oral traditions."


